<h2>Overview</h2><div class="docstring">
  <div class="discussion">
    
<p>This class wraps the logical ConditionVariable class to make it an easier
to work with interface that is similar to Windows&#39; synchronization
events.</p>


  </div>
</div>
<div class="tags">
  

</div>
