<div id="constructor_details" class="method_details_list">
  <h2>Constructor Details</h2>
  
    <div class="method_details first">
  <h3 class="signature first" id="initialize-instance_method">
  
    - (<tt><span class='object_link'><a href="" title="Rex::Sync::Event (class)">Event</a></span></tt>) <strong>initialize</strong>(state = false, auto_reset = true, param = nil) 
  

  

  
</h3><div class="docstring">
  <div class="discussion">
    
<p>Initializes a waitable event.  The state parameter initializes the default
state of the event.  If auto_reset is true, any calls to set() will
automatically reset the event back to an unset state.</p>


  </div>
</div>
